    skos:notation "2202" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Environmentally sustainable information and communication services"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) Minimisation of input waste (other than water and energy) is to be categorised according to the objective that benefits from the improvement of input use.
b) Management of energy consumption from information and communication services is included in Group 1701 Energy efficiency.
c) Waste handling services such as collection, storage, recycling and disposal provided by local councils or private or non-profit waste management businesses are included in Group 1105 Water and waste services."""@en .

