d) Education pertaining to Indigenous communities is included in Division 21 Indigenous."""@en ;
    skos:topConceptOf <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020> .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/1901> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/19> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards understanding impacts of climate change and the development of strategies to adapt to climate change."@en ;
