c) The understanding and provision of education related to Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander populations is included in Group 2102 Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander education Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander education.
d) The understanding and provision of education related to Māori populations is included in Group 2106 Māori education."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2103> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/21> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards the public health of Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islanders. It includes the study of social and cultural factors affecting the health of Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islanders and the delivery of health services to these communities."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020> ;
    skos:narrower <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/210301>,
