        <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/210399> ;
    skos:notation "2103" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander health"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) The diagnosis, prevention and treatment of clinical conditions for non-Indigenous communities is included in Group 2001 Clinical health.
b) Evaluation of health and support services and health policies for non-Indigenous communities is included in Group 2002 Evaluation of health and support services.
c) Provision of health and support services for non-Indigenous communities is included in Group 2003 Provision of health and support services.
d) Health as it pertains to the general population and non-Indigenous communities is included in Group 2004 Public health (excl. specific population health) and Group 2005 Specific population health (excl. Indigenous health)."""@en .

