<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2401> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/24> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards the manufacture of chemical fertilisers and chemicals for the protection of crops and livestock."@en ;
