    skos:notation "2401" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Agricultural chemicals"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) Organic fertilisers and the manufacture of plant extracts which may be used as insecticides or repellents (e.g. pyrethrum) are included in Group 2414 Processed non-food agriculture products (excl. wood, paper and fibre).
b) Manufacture of veterinary pharmaceuticals is included in Group 2416 Veterinary pharmaceutical products."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2408> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/24> ;
