<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/25> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:definition "This division covers R&D which primarily benefits or has application to the exploration, mining, extraction and processing of mineral resources, other than energy mineral resources. It includes R&D directed towards environmentally sustainable exploration, extraction and processing of mineral resources."@en ;
