<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/1503> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/15> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards management and productivity issues. It includes R&D directed towards marketing and industrial relations."@en ;
