    skos:notation "2403" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Ceramics, glass and industrial mineral products"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) Mining, extraction, and first stage processing of stone, clay, sand and ores used for the manufacture of ceramics, glass and industrial mineral products are included in Division 25 Mineral resources (excl. energy resources).
b) Testing the performance and durability and life cycle of building materials is included in Group 1203 Construction materials performance and processes."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2407> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/24> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards the manufacture of structural and sheet metal products, castings, machined and semi-finished fabricated metal products."@en ;
