    skos:notation "2407" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Fabricated metal products"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) Basic metal products is included in Group 2402 Basic metal products (incl. smelting, rolling, drawing and extruding).
b) Prefabrication of metal buildings and manufacture of sheet metal furniture is included in Group 2499 Other manufacturing.
c) Testing of the performance, durability and life cycle of manufactured building materials is included in Division 12 Construction."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2502> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/25> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards processing minerals, other than energy mineral resources."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020> ;
    skos:narrower <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/250201>,
