        <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/260499> ;
    skos:notation "2604" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Harvesting and packaging of plant products"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) Harvesting and transport of forest products is included in Group 2602 Forestry.
b) Improvement of the characteristics, propagation and growing of crops from which these plant products are obtained are included in Groups 2603 Grains and seeds, 2605 Horticultural crops and 2606 Industrial crops.
c) Production of biofuels from plant products is included in Group 1707 Processing of energy sources.
d) Manufacture of products other than biofuels from further processing of these plant products is included in Division 24 Manufacturing.
e) Transportation of plant products other than forest products is included in Division 27 Transport."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2701> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/27> ;
