    skos:prefLabel "Fisheries - aquaculture"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) Improving the characteristics and harvesting of fisheries caught in the wild is included in Group 1003 Fisheries - wild caught.
b) Preparation, handling and storage of unprocessed or minimally processed fish is included in Group 1006 Primary products from animals.
c) Fish welfare and fish products traceability and quality assurance are included in Group 1099 Other animal production.
d) Manufacture of processed fish and seafood products and their primary products is included in Group 2413 Processed food products and beverages (excl. dairy products)."""@en .

