    skos:notation "2104" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander heritage and culture"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) Understanding heritage related to non-Indigenous populations is included in Group 1304 Heritage.
b) Rights to environmental and natural resources is included in Group 1902 Environmental policy, legislation and standards."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2201> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/22> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards fixed line, mobile and satellite communication networks and services. It includes videoconference services."@en ;
