    skos:notation "2201" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Communication technologies, systems and services"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) Development and manufacture of communication equipment is included in Group 2201 Communication technologies, systems and services.
b) Installation of communications networks in buildings is included in Group 1201 Building management and services.
c) Broadcasting is included in Group 2205 Media services."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2411> a skos:Concept ;
