<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/1003> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/10> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards improving the characteristics and harvesting of fisheries caught in the wild for commercial or recreational reasons."@en ;
