    skos:notation "1905" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Understanding climate change"@en ;
    skos:scopeNote """a) Atmosphere and weather, including atmospheric composition are included in Group 1801 Air quality, atmosphere and weather.
b) Strategies relating to adaptation to climate change are included in Group 1901 Adaptation to climate change.
c) Strategies to mitigate climate change are included in Group 1903 Mitigation of climate change.
d) Environmental ethics is included in Group 1303 Ethics."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2002> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/20> ;
