<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2504> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/25> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards mining and extracting minerals, other than energy mineral resources. It includes precious and semi-precious stones and mineral sands."@en ;
