<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/2606> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/26> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards improving the characteristics and growing of crops principally intended for industrial applications such as sugar cane, cotton, wine grapes, tobacco, hemp, cannabis and plants from which essential oils are extracted."@en ;
