    skos:scopeNote """a) Transformation of renewable energy resources into heat, steam or electricity is included in Group 1708 Renewable energy.
b) Engines for use in transport other than internal hydrogen combustion engines are included in Group 2415 Transport equipment."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/1707> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-seo/2020/17> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers R&D directed towards the preparation and supply of energy resources, including the production of hydrogen from other energy sources and biofuel production."@en ;
